• Dropping an image onto the Dock icon now also places it in your magazine design
• Huge speed improvements to update process, which relaunches the updated app
• Informs you if the app has been open and idle for 24 hours
• Some minor revisions to wording in the user interface

Fixed bugs:
• Leaving InDesign open while running the app for the first time now works as expected
• Selecting the cover doesn't open all the templates, just the one you want
• After reading a compatibility notice, quitting the app works as expected 
